'''Maṛtina Hingis''' d tanaddalt n Tennis Taswisit ilulen ass n 30 [[Ctamber]] 1980 di Košice (tamurt n Sluvaki, zikenni čekusluvaki). D nettat id tanaddalt meẓẓilen ig bḍen ad teḥrez talɣuɣa n Grand Chelem si zman n Lottie Dod asegwas 1887, d nettat daɣen id tanaddalt tameẓlant ig bḍen ɣer tqacuct n wedras umaḍan deg umezruy n Tennis.

Tettmeslay Kuz (4) n tutlayin, Tačikit, Talmanit (taswist talmanit), tagyizit d tefṛansist.
Tella d tamdakult n unaddal  n Golf Serǧiu Garsia, sin akkin tessen amyurar n Tennis Radek Stepanek asegwas n 2006. Tezweǧ ak-d umennay afṛansi Tibault Hutin asegwas n 2010.

==Temẓ-is==

Tluled s yisem Martina Hingisová di tmurt n Sluvaki zikenni čekusluvaki, seg mi tesɛa 8 isegwasen Maṛtina tettidir di tmurt Taswist acku yemmas tɛiwed zwaǧ. Deg usegwas n 1999 tuɣ axxam deg temdint n Floride [[Marikan]] maca teqqim tettidir di teswist. D yemma-s is yefkan isem n Maṛtina, imi tella tḥemmel tanadalt tameqṛant n Tennis Maṛtina Navṛatiluva, nettat daɣen n tmurt n čekusluvaki. Yemma-s tella tetturar addal n Tennis, dɣa d ayen itt yeǧǧan attili d tasleɣmayt n Maṛtina deg umecwaṛ ines maṛṛa.

==Amecwaṛ ines seg (1994-2002)==

Maṛtina telmed att urar addal n Tennis si temẓ-is, ɣurs 5 isegwasen di lɛemr-is mi tebda tetturar di tedwilin, tessaweḍ att uɣal d talɣuɣt n umaḍal n tullas asegwas n 1994. asegwas n 1996 turar aked Helena Suková deg uslig n Wimledon, dɣa tuɣal d tanadalt tameẓlant yessawḍen at ḥrez talɣuɣa agi.

Asegwas n 1997 d win ig walan urar n maṛtina ad yuɣal qessaḥ nezzah, tarbaḥ 37 uraren wa deffir wayeḍ, iz d yebwin 6 telɣuɣa, tebwi Open n lustṛali mgal Mary pierce 6-2 6-2, tebweḍ ɣer tagara n Rolland Garros anda texṣer d Iva Majoli acku tuḍen cwiṭ di tagara, tebwi daɣen Wimbledon mgal Novotna aked US Open d Venus Williams 6-4 6-0; d ayen itt yeǧǧan att awi Clem amecṭuḥ.

Tebwi kṛad n talɣiwin n Grand Chelem yemgaraden, ala Rolland Garros it xṣen sin ibardan di tagara, asegwas n 1999 anda turar aked tanadalt tameqṛant [[Steffi Graf]] ig llan di tagara n'umecwaṛ ines deg addal n Tennis, teqqimed deg umezruy, acku Maṛtina tɛac asenni yiwen wass ur tezmir attettu, tella tarbaḥ urar deg aḥric amezwaru, sinna yellad umgarad garas d unefray, ayen yeǧǧan ula d-imfarǧen (imeshanayen) ad ddun d [[Steffi Graf]], di tagara, Maṛtina texṣer talɣuɣa, teffeɣ seg urar s-imeṭṭawen, ayen werǧin n wala deg addal agi.
Seg ass nni Maṛtina ut tebwi talɣuɣa n Grand chelem, teqqim deg umḍiq amezwaru deg ubellez umaḍal, acku trbbaḥ aṭas n telɣuɣa it tturar, maca ur tebwi ara talɣuɣa tameqṛant.

